{"tid":1716951,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"佔領區既手足請保持自肅！！","createTime":"2019-11-13T13:08:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T13:14:58.000Z","uid":56260,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"675121a5517de04a8efa47a96688d444a2599211","tid":1716951,"uid":56260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T13:08:08.000Z","msg":"下一秒隨時係戰場黎架<br />\n唔好掉以輕心<br />\n亦唔好俾外界解讀錯誤氣氛同印象<br />\n唔係暴大又會即刻變返左膠大學架喇<br />\n好重要架<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">願榮光歸香港</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">大家要有個心態係真係打緊仗。一係抖下，一係練習下，一係就幫下手準備嘢，唔好玩住啦！以下係中大守軍嘅吐糟：\n\n⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️\n\n「中大人表示有樣野好不吐不快。\n\n可唔可以幫手出post叫下中大夏鼎基運動場班小朋友唔好再嘉年華唔好再快樂抗爭。\n\n有班小朋友不停揸住架剷草機兜勻成個運動場，掛住玩又唔睇路，前面有把爛遮都照碌過，仲要未停定架機就想徒手執，知唔知咩叫危險🤕\n\n仲有用電單車係運動場兜風個啲，完全唔知佢做緊乜。\n踢波個啲，好多手足係運動場上面休息緊，班友不停射龍門，啲波周圍飛省到其他人，有力氣不如去討論行動，去掟下水樽練下掉火魔好過啦。」</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V5USzCX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV5USzCX.png&h=288f3608&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b6vFJwm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb6vFJwm.png&h=4132be17&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"058043d5a1187670af535aa5513eca50009d3a6f","tid":1716951,"uid":56260,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T13:09:49.000Z","msg":"唔係指責<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但要注意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bab05e8efa3e1e927f64089f7a1e6f02a2111011","tid":1716951,"uid":34869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T13:11:19.000Z","msg":"丫屌果個「中大人」<br />\n人地成班士兵響戰場, 自己響冷氣房呢樣果樣"},{"pid":"0e9ee4436ef83e875af0aae0ebba11fedee68a71","tid":1716951,"uid":63670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T13:14:06.000Z","msg":"收皮啦！<br />\n下一刻可能就係開真槍！<br />\n難聽d講都唔知有無聽日<br />\n放鬆下唔畀？<br />\n有意見就出去幫手啦！講！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />依家又唔係好似黑警感強姦殺人<br />\n打下波都唔畀！"},{"pid":"c74bc0e636ca61ce7c3fb7c4c9d9a658758025c8","tid":1716951,"uid":56260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bab05e8efa3e1e927f64089f7a1e6f02a2111011","tid":1716951,"uid":34869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T13:11:19.000Z","msg":"丫屌果個「中大人」<br />\n人地成班士兵響戰場, 自己響冷氣房呢樣果樣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T13:14:21.000Z","msg":"我知現場手足係明既 呢個係肯定既<br />\n所以我唔係指責<br />\n但好多人睇完會自行解讀 注意下者"},{"pid":"d3a1ac98d156986d5f1a1d902546786f103cb78f","tid":1716951,"uid":63670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T13:14:58.000Z","msg":"可能語氣重左<br />\n但係真係唔好再講了,<br />\n珍惜佢哋好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}